+/*
+ * @brief Compute the negative inner product distance between two int8 vectors.
+ * @param x Pointer to the first input int8 vector.
+ * @param y Pointer to the second input int8 vector.
+ * @param d Length of the vectors.
+ * @param dis Stores the inner product result (int32_t).
+ * @param dis_size Length of dis.
+ */
